Date: Sun, 28 Jun 2026 22:44:05 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] feat: add dashboard today mode

Adds a Today Mode / Full Dashboard toggle to the Dashboard. Today Mode
surfaces only the sections needed for immediate daily study decisions:
backup warning, Next Assessment, Assessment Prep Progress, Weekly Review,
Today's Study Growth, Battle Plan, and Marks-at-Risk. Full Dashboard
restores all sections. Preference persists via baccllb-dashboard-view-mode.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
